{
  "stem": "748.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this what we ate a couple days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not much, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yoli was the-- she give a-- a little bit, and just have something in the body.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we passed German cities-- small, you know-- then the-- the German families threw bread, and clothes, blankets of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the SS shoot them, shoot through the windows, because they shouldn't do this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SHAKES HEAD] You know, you have to have [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] too much pens and paper to describe what a person can feel and can do it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes, [EMOTIONAL] I can't sleep, because it comes always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I think, my God how I did that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This is un-possible-- no soap, not a-- a clean towel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I broke-- a SS woman break my leg with a iron stick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't got nothing to make a band-aid, to put this-- I knew it from mine nursing qualification.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, I took a dirty shirt off from me and make band-aid and put together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She give me with that stick, because I couldn't walk quick, like she was-- she wanted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, still.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, I survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, when-- when they started the talk in--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked, and we was-- every minute, you heard in the-- in-- in-- in the back-- [MAKES GUN SHOT NOISES].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shot the people because, if they can't walk, what can a soldier do there?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would not take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Women and men, together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Awful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They give a couple coats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, one thing what was, they sew in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we founded there diamonds, in the-- in the clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
